Package common.message.synchronization

Interface IUpdateMemberListData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDataPacketData, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IUpdateMemberListAddData, IUpdateMemberListRemoveData
    public interface IUpdateMemberListData
extends IDataPacketData
    This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the request to update a member's local instance of a group's member list with a list of members in order to ensure a fully connected P2P graph network.
    Author:
    Stephanie Yang, Makoto Jankovsky
